<% provide(:title, t('International camps')) %>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <p class="col-sm-7 static">
      On the eve of the summer holiday, parents usually ask themselves how to organize their children's holiday as
      interesting and effective as possible because everyone wants time for fun, sports, socializing, but also for
      growth, for example, in studying a foreign language. The ideal solution could be a trip to one of the
      international linguistic centers where children would familiarise with the country's history and culture, make
      new friends from all corners of the world and realize that a foreign language must and can be mastered a lot
      easier, in the captivating lessons organized by native speakers.
    </p>
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <%= image_tag 'international_3.jpg', alt: "Picture", class: 'img-fluid img-static' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <p class="col-sm-7 static">
      ISCEO gives parents the chance to fulfill their wishes and invites children and young adults (aged 9-19) to
      attend summer schools organized in the UK, Europe and the US. You can choose from the programs we offer,
      depending on the language you want to learn, your age and your preferred country. This offer targets both
      individuals and groups.
    </p>
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <%= image_tag 'international_1.jpg', alt: "Picture", class: 'img-fluid img-static img-hidden' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <%= image_tag 'international_4.jpg', alt: "Picture", class: 'img-fluid img-static' %>
    </div>
    <div class="static col-sm-7">
      <p class="static-accademic">
        By opting for ISCEO services, you have the unique opportunity to combine language learning with relaxation, fun
        and exciting excursions. The organizers assume the responsibility of supporting parents in preparing the set of
        necessary travel documents and accompanying children to the program (on a group trip), which, over our ten years
        of activity, has proved to be a important factor in ensuring a favorable psychological climate for both children
        and their parents.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <%= image_tag 'international_2.jpg', alt: "Picture", class: 'img-fluid img-static img-hidden' %>
    </div>
    <div class="static col-sm-7">
      <p class="static-accademic">
        At the end of the program, the participants obtain a certificate reflecting the linguistic progress during the
        course, attesting to the current level of competence and linguistic performance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>